<h2> Hardware // LEDs HB &amp; IN &amp; OUT  </h2><p> The LEDs
HB, IN and OUT can be configured via the <code>/proc</code> 
filesystem to fit your needs. At system boot the HB LED will
be configured by the OPTION parameter in 
<code>/etc/sysconfig/leds</code>. </p><p><pre>
